messages.content:
Good day,
Please be informed that I just sent the proposal to this email, kindly check and advice your acceptance. Thank you.

Chetiya - thank you very much for reaching out. Please email Tavish tavish@carinahardy.com with all the details.

Love seeing what's going on at nuanu - always exciting.

Dear Carina Hardy,
I hope you are in good spirits.

My name is Chetiya Riswan and I am the Sales & Marketing of HARMONY - A Social Wellness Complex. 

Stage one of the complex is a Spa & Restaurant launching July 2024, set in a lush tropical forest in the heart of Nuanu City (www.nuanu.com), Nyanyi, Tabanan, Bali. 
Worth noting, we will be a Tirta III licensed spa, one of only three in Bali, along with The St. Regis Bali Resort and Jumeirah Bali.

I am reaching out to discuss a potential consignment partnership with your company. Could you please direct me to the appropriate contact person?

Look forward to hearing from you.

share.share_text: Comprising a total of 9 functional areas in at Nuanu we are creating a future destination, a sustainable space with a regenerative mindset for living and working.
